snippet.title: Character Teaser - "Sangonomiya Kokomi: The Ocean's Will" | Genshin Impact
snippet.description:
As the heir to the Sangonomiya line, she bears the responsibility of heeding the wishes of Watatsumi Island's people.
Just as how the situation in battle can change a lot, so too can people's hearts. Faced with this, Kokomi knows that she has a long road ahead of her.
